      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <h1
          class="code text-5xl text-white sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl"
        >
          404
        </h1>
        <p class="mb-2 mt-3 lg:text-3xl">
          We have a problem.
        </p>
        <p class="body">
          We couldnâ€™t find that link.<br class="sm:hidden" /> Check the address or
          <a href="/" class="underline hover:text-red-500">head back home</a>.
